  大兴安岭北段阿里河地区1:5万土壤地球化学不同粒级样品对比研究
  A Comparative Study of 1:50,000 Soil Geochemical Samples of Different Grain Sizes in Ali River Region, Northern Part of the Greater Khingan Mountains
 
